Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of NiO-SDC/SDC anode was studied.
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace

Sentencas: The anode was compacted by pressing, after which sintering was conducted in a conventional furnace at 1200 degrees C. A high-energy ball mill was used to mix the Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9(SDC) nanopowder and NiO.
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace

Sentencas: A pressing technique was applied to fabricate the NiO-SDC/SDC anode cells.
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace

Sentencas: The effect of different compaction pressures (200, 300, and 400 MPa) on the performance of the anodes was investigated via electrochemical impedance spectroscopy at an intermediate temperature range (600-800 degrees C).
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace

Sentencas: The nanoindentation technique and Archimedes method, which were used to measure stiffness and bulk density, respectively, revealed that increases in porosity were correlated with decreases in compaction pressure.
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace

Sentencas: High electrochemical performance can be achieved if the compaction pressure is decreased and the operating temperature is increased because of hydrogen spillover during the operation.
Titulo: Effect of compaction pressure on the performance of a non-symmetrical NiO-SDC/SDC composite anode fabricated by conventional furnace
